  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cognitive profile of patients who suffer both from PTSD and OCD, as compared to those who
      suffer from PTSD or OCD without other comorbidity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Demographic data and cognitive data will be compared on PTSD, PTSD-OCD and OCD patients using
      a battery of computerized cognitive tests
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
